show.title: Unscripted Romance: In Love With My Substitute Wife

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Yvette Taylor agrees to marry into the powerful Jones family in place of her sister, setting off a journey of sacrifice and self-discovery. Caught in a web of family duty and unexpected love, she forms a complicated bond with her new husband. Spanning 100 episodes, this romantic drama explores identity, resilience, and the pursuit of true affection.
